{"tid":874313,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"諗返起以前學校禁電話嘅年代","createTime":"2018-10-24T06:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T10:03:20.000Z","uid":46527,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"543955c938255a074576c6d65fb8ca2754cc18e0","tid":874313,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:14:21.000Z","msg":"睇到而家啲中學生電話一手一部，諗返起以前學校仲係禁電話嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n雖然學校唔係會check袋，但見到你用都係會沒收。<br />\n<br />\n以前中史科補課，個老師係訓導組嘅老師。補課開始點人頭，有人未到，個老師就叫<br />\n<br />\n「搵人打電話問XXX喺邊？」<br />\n<br />\n成班人心諗，想裝我地彈弓？<br />\n<br />\n「我地無帶電話啊！」（其實個個都有）<br />\n<br />\n然後全場dead air <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問到第三次老師話當睇唔到先有一個人拎電話搵返遲到個同學，咁就搞左10分鐘"},{"pid":"ecfb4a02f43eb5df239db4d46abcee4c52b45fa1","tid":874313,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":22,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95b37ac034d47058b4bfaca5df695c71db1118db","tid":874313,"uid":77171,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"每次收埋偷偷地用都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又驚又想用"},{"pid":"7672f7ab72300fd8b857c44d4f38ae5cde750574","tid":874313,"uid":46347,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"有次右手係櫃桶玩緊電話 個呀sir問邊有個做功課就舉手 下意識舉手舉埋部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9c3586e8bde93955ab17296faf5f5594ae00e5","tid":874313,"uid":172914,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7672f7ab72300fd8b857c44d4f38ae5cde750574","tid":874313,"uid":46347,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"有次右手係櫃桶玩緊電話 個呀sir問邊有個做功課就舉手 下意識舉手舉埋部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class